and moral integrity.

625
00:48:35,871 --> 00:48:40,042
This is putting the true meaning
of education into practice.

626
00:48:41,501 --> 00:48:46,255
<i>However, the current education system
of our country has strayed too far</i>

627
00:48:46,256 --> 00:48:48,467
