628
00:48:49,968 --> 00:48:52,888
<i>Nonetheless, in the midst of this reality,</i>

629
00:48:53,847 --> 00:48:57,767
<i>most teachers in this country
continue to fulfill their calling,</i>

630
00:48:57,768 --> 00:49:01,688
<i>teaching children and trying to guide them
toward the right path.</i>

