635
00:49:24,836 --> 00:49:28,382
The ERPB will uphold
the value of education

636
00:49:29,174 --> 00:49:30,676
and protect victims...

637
00:49:32,594 --> 00:49:35,847
until schools are no longer places
of fear and anxiety

638
00:49:36,598 --> 00:49:38,265
