00:57:26,985 --> 00:57:28,778
You should've stopped then.

783
00:57:29,571 --> 00:57:33,616
It's adults like you
who turn young students into monsters.

784
00:57:34,117 --> 00:57:37,120
If you can't be a good adult,
at least don't be a bad one.

785
00:57:38,121 --> 00:57:40,706
And what about you? Are you a good adult?

786
00:57:40,707 --> 00:57:43,710
You think I won't find anything on you?
Damn...

787
00:57:57,599 --> 00:57:58,433
I guess

788
00:58:00,018 --> 00:58:03,188
I'm not a good adult either.

789
